Title : Wikipedia:WikiProject Opera/OotM/August2014
Text : [[File:Christoph-Willibald-Gluck.jpg|right|100px]]
'''The Composer of the Month for August is [[Christoph Willibald Gluck]]. This year marks the tercentenary of his birth.'''

We lack articles on several of his early operas, including...
*''[[Le nozze d'Ercole e d'Ebe]]'' (1747)
*''[[L'île de Merlin, ou Le monde renversé]]'' (1758)

We also lack articles on three of his librettists...
*[[François-Louis Gand Le Bland Du Roullet]]  (1716-1786) 
*[[Jean-Baptiste-Louis-Théodore de Tschudi]] (1734–1784)
*[[Francesco Vanneschi]] (''floruit'' 1732–1759)
